# TipCalculator

This is a Tip Calculator application for iOS submitted as the [pre-assignment](https://gist.github.com/timothy1ee/7747214) requirement for CodePath.

Time spent: 8 hours

Completed:

* [DONE] Required: User can enter a bill amount, choose a tip percentage, and see the tip and total values.
* [DONE] Required: Settings page to change the default tip percentage.
* [DONE] Optional: UI animations, messages will show up when default tip percentage changes, disappear when tap on empty space
* [DONE] Optional: Add update theme color feature to setting page

